      "description": "Интервал свечи и допустимый промежуток запроса:\n- 1min [1 minute, 1 day]\n- 2min [2 minutes, 1 day]\n- 3min [3 minutes, 1 day]\n- 5min [5 minutes, 1 day]\n- 10min [10 minutes, 1 day]\n- 15min [15 minutes, 1 day]\n- 30min [30 minutes, 1 day]\n- hour [1 hour, 7 days]\n- day [1 day, 1 year]\n- week [7 days, 2 years]\n- month [1 month, 10 years]\n",
      "type": "string",
      "enum": [
        "1min",
        "2min",
        "3min",
        "5min",
        "10min",
        "15min",
        "30min",
        "hour",
        "day",
        "week",
        "month"
      ]
    },
